reviewText: The participants share excellent, emotional personal reflections and experiences.  I really like this DVD!  Thank you!
Helps greatly with Rosary meditations and it is interesting to hear of these Catholics stories of faith.

Excellent. I was asked to teach the rosary to youth group at my parish. DVD Rosary Stars was the star of the talk.  I gave them a Rosary CD to take home and they were disappointed that it was not from the Rosary Stars.
